OL,6,FThey both feature a combination of
OL,7,Fprivate cabins beds ` which are sold
OL,8,Fat a premium price ` and regular train
OL,9,Fseats, which many passengers select to
OL,10,Fsave money but find difficult to sleep
OL,11,Fon.
OL,13,FFuture Travel Studio said DreamSuite
OL,14,Fhad been created as a "middle-ground
OL,15,Foption".
OL,17,FIt claimed this could offer 60% more
OL,18,Fcapacity than sleeper cabins ` meaning
OL,19,Fsavings could be passed on to
OL,20,Fpassengers ` and be more comfortable
OL,21,Fthan conventional seating.
