OL,3,CTrain seat that can be converted into
OL,4,Cbed revealed
OL,6,FThe seat can be converted from an
OL,7,Fupright position to a flat bed with a
OL,8,Flength of six feet and two inches
OL,9,Fusing a mechanical system.
OL,11,FIt features a privacy screen `
OL,12,Fenabling flexibility for solo
OL,13,Ftravellers and couples ` and space to
OL,14,Fhang clothes and store bags.
OL,16,FIt has been designed to meet UK rail
OL,17,Fsafety standards, and could be fitted
OL,18,Fto existing carriages.
