OL,6,FDesigner Nik Lusardi, whose previous
OL,7,Froles include creating Virgin
OL,8,FAtlantic's first-class seats between
OL,9,F2004 and 2016, said: "What we've been
OL,10,Ftrying to do is democratise this kind
OL,11,Fof product on rails.
OL,13,F"We want to make this attainable for
OL,14,Feverybody, not just business
OL,15,Fpassengers and people who've got deep
OL,16,Fpockets."
