OL,6,FHe said DreamSuite was a "game change"
OL,7,Fas his experience of UK trains was
OL,8,Fthat the seats are "all a bit hard,
OL,9,Fthey get uncomfortable after about
OL,10,Fhalf-an-hour".
OL,12,FHe added: "We are very passionate
OL,13,Fabout sustainability.
OL,15,F"We think there's a bit of a tsunami
OL,16,Fcoming around this kind of product.
OL,18,F"People are gravitating more towards
OL,19,Ftrain. This product makes train travel
OL,20,Fa more compelling argument."
