OL,6,FAlstom managing director for the UK
OL,7,Fand Ireland Nick Crossfield said: "By
OL,8,Fintegrating advanced, flexible seating
OL,9,Foptions into existing rolling stock,
OL,10,Fwe're helping to unlock new
OL,11,Fopportunities for both daytime and
OL,12,Fnight-time rail services while
OL,13,Fsupporting the industry's efforts to
OL,14,Freduce carbon emissions.
OL,16,F"DreamSuite truly is a game-changer."
